{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, student composition samples, gathered in collaboration with schools, cover a wide range of educational stages from elementary to university.",
    "These samples contain various error types and writing styles, making them ideal training materials for the error correction and improvement suggestion modules.",
    "After collecting the raw texts, thorough preprocessing and annotation are carried out.",
    "The texts are cleaned by removing HTML tags, special characters, and unnecessary spaces to ensure they are in plain text format.",
    "Tokenization splits the text into meaningful units, and the WordPiece method handles out-of-vocabulary words."
  ]
}